OL,5, Young black scientists will get        
OL,6, sizeable grants towards cutting-edge   
OL,7, research in a pilot scheme aimed at    
OL,8, increasing their numbers in the field. 
OL,10,FFive scientists a year will get up to  
OL,11,F#690,000 spread over four years.       
OL,13,FThe Royal Society, which represents the
OL,14,FUK's leading researchers, hopes its    
OL,15,Fgrants increase low numbers of black   
OL,16,Fscientists, particularly in research.  
OL,18,FThe fellowships should allow the       
OL,19,Frecipients to work in any of the       
OL,20,Fcountry's research institutes.         
